---
title: Chilli Jam-Roasted Pork Belly & Fried Rice with Sesame Soy Cabbage & Ponzu Garlicky Greens
description: Zingy, sweet and packed with umami, our chilli jam is the perfect glaze for tender, slow-cooked pork belly. Freshen the dish up
with crunchy cabbage, coated in a sesame-soy dressing and you're on your way to an unforgettable fusion dinner!
